text: Agustin Gómez (born 28 August 1996) is an Argentine professional footballer who plays as a centre back for Defensores Unidos. ==Career== Gómez spent time in the youth system of Racing Club, prior to joining Defensa y Justicia. On 26 July 2017, Gómez joined Allsvenskan side AIK on loan until December 2017. He made his professional debut on 23 August 2017 during a Svenska Cupen victory away to Värmbols. He returned to Defensa y Justicia in 2018 after no league appearances for AIK, though he was an unused substitute eight times.
